reviewText: Got this for D.E.B.S. after seeing the feature film I had to own the original short too!  Very entertaining concept and charming execution.  I am enjoying watching the other films too, it's quite a lot of content for a good price.  I would recommend it to anyone.

Even though myself I have Never gotten in real life to see real lesbians kissing and holding hands! Lesbians are the most special kinda girls in the world to me. I Never get tired of watching lesbian romance in the movies!
